[src:architecture-patterns/service-oriented-architecture] A topic that has experienced extensive coverage involves the relationship between Web 2.0 and service-oriented architectures.
[src:architecture-patterns/service-oriented-architecture] SOA is the philosophy of encapsulating application logic in services with a uniformly defined interface and making these publicly available via discovery mechanisms.
